        },
        {
            "title": "小額包裹免稅時代告終之後 Shein在美國的強勁成長戛然而止",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OhGGxq.WePAPSd95drihcg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/416cf254172717027a297f4578ff09ba\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 自從曾推動Shein Group Ltd成長的美國小額包裹關稅豁免政策被川普政府終止以來，這家迅速擴張的零售商在美國的銷售受到了衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項政策於8月29日結束；Bloomberg Second Measure的數據顯示，9月Shein的銷售額較去年同期下降了約8%，錄得過去三年來第二差的月度表現。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/61.QE719gSrLxUIWAy5gXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ef4d7e774b29eb92f9461028407e4e8c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普政府已經表示，其不再允許價值不超過800美元的包裹免稅入境的原因之一，是要給美國企業創造公平的競爭環境。Shein是一家非上市公司，成立於中國內地，現在總部位於新加坡。近年來，該公司依靠在亞洲製造的商品、用低價壓制競爭對手，從而得以迅速發展壯大。彭博新聞社在7月報導稱，今年頭三個月該公司的季度銷售額接近100億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6c60e2f5-5ae4-3b8c-be93-1b165d4c0e13-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博行業研究零售電商高級分析師Poonam Goyal稱，小額包裹免稅政策終結將有利於Shein在快時尚領域的競爭對手。該領域的其他巨頭包括H&amp;M和Zara。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小額包裹不再免稅，「競爭環境已經變得公平了，」Goyal表示。「這意味著他們的價格不再像過去那麼有競爭力了。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Shein未回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Shein’s Robust US Growth Evaporates After Trump Tariff Hit</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E9%A1%8D%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E5%85%8D%E7%A8%85%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%B5%82%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C-shein%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E6%88%9B%E7%84%B6%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%A2-071500089.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 16:41:02",
